tool_description: Get the basic metadata on all breeds of cats from around the world.
name: CatBreedDB
title: CatBreedDB

api_list.name: Paginated
api_list.description: Get all cat breed results in a set of 10 per page.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://catbreeddb.p.rapidapi.com/paginated/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "catbreeddb.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
